01:01:51,120 --> 01:02:00,320
I think Alyasha makes this quick wrong move just because he doesn't, he wants, Dostoevsky wants to get the Grand Inquisitor story in here.

698
01:02:00,320 --> 01:02:11,600
And it's true that it's not clear what right move Alyasha at this stage of his innocence and his youth and so forth and lack of understanding of the world could make.

