717
01:04:09,399 --> 01:04:12,680
And that's part of what I think.

718
01:04:12,680 --> 01:04:32,600
Another thing that is not just me, it's clear that Dostoevsky thinks that in order to really help people, you've got to have experience the dark side and have evil in your past, which you integrated and overcome, but which you understand, because it's still part of you.

